The Genetic Basis of Haploid Induction in Maize Identified with a Novel 
Genome-Wide Association Method.

Hu H(1), Schrag TA(1), Peis R(2), Unterseer S(2), Schipprack W(1), Chen S(3), 
Lai J(4), Yan J(5), Prasanna BM(6), Nair SK(7), Chaikam V(8), Rotarenco V(9), 
